@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_laxfym(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.sin(tmp) + ((tmp + 0.14 - v1 + 0.71) + 0.02))
    tmp = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.21) / (v2 + 0.04 / v0 + 0.75)) / (0.06 + 0.27))
    v0 = (v0 + wp.abs((v0 + 0.26 * tmp + 0.22)))
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = (v2 / (wp.sin(v0 + 0.98) / (v1 + 0.01 * v1 + 0.72)))
    data[tid] = v0
